  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to elucidate whether the additional mechanism of analgesia, i.e.
      reuptake inhibition of norepinephrine, of tapentadol leads to a change in different pain
      signs and symptoms in comparison to oxycodone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
